                  ref="#pmb11988">Kraus</rs> – Dr. <rs type="person"
                  ref="#pmb39325">Pisk</rs>
               <lb xml:id="uuid_c060099b-9e76-475b-a98b-bb9e23c74cc6"/>exp. 1.3.1930.</note>
         </p>
